Asgardian has a large (and expandable) set of words that can be used as frames. For ease of learning, these are broken into the following categories.

* [[Time|Tenses]]
* [[Aspect|Aspect]]
* Space
* Direction
* Reality
* [[Modality / possible worlds ("should"/"could")|Modal frames]]
* [[Discourse|Discourse frames]]
* [[Set membership|Set membership frames]]
